Create a java project
Add the MR jar files -> external libraries
hadoop2.7.2/share/hadoop/

common/ 3jarfiles
common/lib -> all jar files
share/hadoop/hdfs  jarfiles
share/hadoop/mapreduce -> jarfiles
share/hadoop/yarn -> jar files

Write Mapper class -> map method
Write Reducer class -> reduce method
Driver -> main method 
compile the java -> package them into Jar file
Execute this jar file -> submit the job to RM.
